snippet.title: Best of NFL Stars on Bar Rescue 🏈
snippet.description:
From bar owners like Marshawn Lynch to recon spies like Chris Long, NFL stars regularly pop up on Bar Rescue — here are some of their best moments.  

Bar Rescue now has its own YouTube Channel! Subscribe here for all the latest Bar Rescue content: https://bit.ly/3ayie64

#BarRescue #ParamountNetwork

Jon Taffer embarks on a cross-country tour of the worst drinking establishments in America. Bad drinks, wild staffs, and wasted owners conspire against him and his experts as they give failing businesses one last shot at success.
